      "description": "Affordable entry point with plenty of potential, this vehicle is being offered as a straightforward, budget-friendly option for buyers who value price and opportunity. It presents as a sensible choice for basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a hands-on project, delivering practical value at a compelling price. If you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive way into ownership, this is a chance worth considering.",
