      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runner with plenty of potential for someone who wants cheap transport, a handy backup, or a project to tinker with. Priced fairly for what it is, and a great chance to get on the road without spending big. If you want something straightforward and budget-friendly, this one\u2019s well worth a look.",
